{"tid":2177440,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲試過打類固醇針/激光去疤","createTime":"2020-08-27T17:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T17:25:35.000Z","uid":115239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"197205faabe170ef6d42f9ad76a9d2e8a84d5c02","tid":2177440,"uid":115239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"我係絲 早排意外係小腿聯左6針 <br />\n留低左條疤 深啡色凸起 成條百足咁<br />\n<br />\n口就話唔介意 <br />\n但依家出街都係唔覺唔覺就執條長褲著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一黎唔想比人望 <br />\n二黎唔可以曬條疤 因為超易色素沉澱<br />\n到時就搽幾多除疤膏都冇用<br />\n<br />\n我本身好鍾意戶外活動 <br />\n跑步行山wakesurf樣樣都鍾意<br />\n因為條疤冇得曬真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搽除疤膏同痴除疤貼都冇乜起色<br />\n先開始上網搵 原來可以打類固醇針/激光治療<br />\n所以想上黎問下有冇巴打絲打<br />\n有冇做過類似既野 又有醫生推介 <br />\n唔想比人湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84145c1dbf9d192e9f6824b48dc0c23c0921bdf6","tid":2177440,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"有幾大條呀 睇過"},{"pid":"14ab2882cacbef2934f49ee6f209eaf23651cd18","tid":2177440,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84145c1dbf9d192e9f6824b48dc0c23c0921bdf6","tid":2177440,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"有幾大條呀 睇過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:22:22.000Z","msg":"雙刀火雞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fe3a30ae03574caea879fd194b7de4545e64a4","tid":2177440,"uid":216888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:44:03.000Z","msg":"無人會理依d"},{"pid":"d54c74e8ecec3dacd1835f2786a4ab9225c98215","tid":2177440,"uid":115239,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"84145c1dbf9d192e9f6824b48dc0c23c0921bdf6","tid":2177440,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"有幾大條呀 睇過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:53:28.000Z